## 2. 下载zip 解压

- 这里直接到scripts文件夹中执行这两个脚本就好了
  - uninstall-all-users.vbs
  - install-all-users.vbs

![image-20240528231049053](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RabbitFeng/TyporaPic/master/images/image-20240528231049053.png)
